作曲家 Bear McCreary 宣布与 Slash、Corey Taylor 等人合作的新专辑https://www.nme.com/news/music/composer-bear-mccreary-announces-new-album-featuring-slash-corey-taylor-and-more-3593432?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=composer-bear-麦克里宣布新专辑收录了斜线科里泰勒等人Surej SinghTue, 27 Feb 2024 06:16:50 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3593432 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/slash-bear-mccreary-corey-taylor@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/slash-bear-mccreary-corey-taylor@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/slash-bear-mccreary-corey-taylor@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/slash-bear-mccreary-corey-taylor@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/slash-bear-mccreary-corey-taylor@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/slash-bear-mccreary-corey-taylor@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/slash-bear-mccreary-corey-taylor@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>专辑中的其他主唱还有 Rufus Wainwright、System Of A Down 的 Serj Tankian 等</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/composer-bear-mccreary-announces-new-album-featuring-slash-corey-taylor-and-more-3593432">作曲家 Bear McCreary 宣布与 Slash、Corey Taylor 等人合作的新专辑</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/slash-bear-mccreary-corey-taylor@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/slash-bear-mccreary-corey-taylor@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/slash-bear-mccreary-corey-taylor@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/slash-bear-mccreary-corey-taylor@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/slash-bear-mccreary-corey-taylor@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/slash-bear-mccreary-corey-taylor@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/slash-bear-mccreary-corey-taylor@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>著名电影和视频游戏作曲家 Bear McCreary 宣布推出一张名为“The Singularity”的个人专辑，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slash">Slash</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/corey-taylor">Corey Taylor</a>等人。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/idles-tangk-album-review-lyrics-3586056">Idles – “Tangk”评论：我们见过的最开放的评论</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周末，麦克雷在社交媒体上分享了《The Singularity》的预告片，该专辑将于 5 月 10 日发行。即将发行的专辑以由鲁弗斯·温赖特 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rufus-wainwright">Rufus Wainwright)</a>主演的主打单曲《Type III》进行了预览。</p><p>根据<a href="https://bearmccreary.com/TheSingularity/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">McCreary 的官方网站</a>，确认出现在专辑中的还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/system-of-a-down">System Of A Down</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/serj-tankian">Serj Tankian</a> 、Joe Satriani、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soundgarden">Soundgarden</a>的 Kim Thayil、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anthrax">Anthrax</a>的 Scott Ian、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/meshuggah">Meshuggah</a>的 Jens Kidman、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-dillinger-escape-plan">The Dillinger Escape Plan</a>的Ben Weinman、The Aristocrat 的 Guthrie Govan 和 Bryan Beller、Blue Öyster Cult 的 Buck Dharma 等。 </p><p><iframe title="Ⅲ型" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/I2ayh5720zo?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>贝尔·麦克雷还确认将推出附带的<em>《奇点》</em>图画小说，其中一个名叫蓝眼睛的角色必须逃离永生的魔掌，才能拯救他身边的人。</p><p> 5 月 12 日（星期日），Bear McCreary 将在洛杉矶方达剧院现场表演“奇点”。门票<a href="https://www.axs.com/events/532800/bear-mccreary-tickets" target="_blank" rel="noopener">现已发售</a>，但目前尚不清楚还有谁将与他一起演出。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C3sglDwO5dx/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,